    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the measurement of a material’s ability to deflect light, and is the ratio of the speed of light in a vacuum to the speed of light in the material.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
